          starterCode: 'class CorrelationEngine {\n  constructor(windowMs) {\n    // Your code here\n  }\n  \n  addEvent(event) {\n    // Your code here - أضف حدث وحاول تطبيق القواعد\n  }\n  \n  addRule(rule) {\n    // Your code here\n  }\n}',
