          starterCode: 'class ApiMonitor {\n  track(apiKey, endpoint) {\n    // Your code here\n  }\n  \n  checkViolations(apiKey) {\n    // Your code here\n  }\n  \n  getRateLimit(apiKey) {\n    // Your code here - أرجع المتبقي\n  }\n}',
